message.body: Youre still out with jimmy?
Yea. Everything ok?
Yea I was just wondering that's all. I guess you're having a good time then? Seeing how complaining all week that you didn't want to go turned into 6+ hour event.
Well hes talking im ready though lol
Wait! Your still at the restaurant?
Sitting outside in the car. Idk why he cant just drive and talk. Im tired! Lol
Finally! Were driving I'm coming home. Lol I did have a good time though. Was nice to catch up
Omg so how long where you in the car for? Like 4 hours?

No we were at the restaurant for a while. We closed the place down. Went to pietros. Didn't leave until I said "you know they are closing right"? I thought that meant we would have went straight home but he decided to continue the conversation on for forever.
And im just sitting here like dude im gonna dart so loud when i get out of this car!
Omg a dead cat!!!
Ew where?
Laying between two parked cars on 10th between shunk and porter
Ew!
Would you want a meatball sandwich to go? Gram said she'll make it you can pick it up.
No im full but thanks
I hate abu im getting rid of him.
Y now?
He is getting aggressive. Attacked me so the first and last time. He is lucky to be alive right now
How so? Like what did he do?
He just bear hugged the shit out of my arm and tried the shred my hand to pieces like a piranha.
9th st closed. .. eargasm closed. Went to fairhill
Finally a breather four orders on the board when I got back but that's because they pulled two drivers from the West location
Oh wow! That sucks though. Cause it took money from u.
Yeah but everyone that I was delivering was at an hour and 30 minutes to an hour and 45 minutes so people were waiting in almost 2 hours for their food
Yea but thats what u get when u order on super bowl sunday
We legit needed the help

Yeah but apparently not everybody knows that because some customers were actually calling the store complaining that they were waiting too long when they were only waiting an hour and they were warned that it would be an hour and a half
Wow people are assholes. Have you counted money recently? U know what I've made so far?
Nah but when I dropped 2 hours ago I think I had close to $50. I should be ready to drop again
Thats pretty good then cause you did a good amount of delivering after that.
I did 19 deliveries so far
If brooke still wants to order, one order on board lol js. I just left with two
I left already. Text her
Nah bec I should have told her about 40 mins ago.
She went to bed already anyway
